Some Lesser Known Facts About Prabhleen Sandhu

Prabhleen Sandhu started her career as a Punjabi film actress.

Some of her popular Punjabi movies are ‘Yaaran Naal Baharan’, ‘Ek Jind Ek Jaan’, ‘Rahe Chardi Kala Punjab Di’, ‘Ishq Garaari’, etc.

Prabhleen has appeared in the TV serials- ‘Apki Antara’, ‘Mohe Rang De’, ‘Crime Patrol’, etc.

She has also worked in the Hindi movies such as ‘Shahid’, ‘Sixteen’, ‘Not a Love Story’, ‘FryDay’, etc.

Prabhleen has worked in many TVC ads.

In 2017, she was seen in the web series ‘Akki Vikki Te Nikki’.
